        <updateDate>2019-08-16T18:43:19Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Protect and Serve Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill amends the federal criminal code to add a new section that imposes criminal penalties on a person who knowingly causes (or attempts to cause) bodily injury to a person based on the actual or perceived status of the person as a law enforcement officer.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
